item.description:
&ldquo;Dashboard&rdquo;
Select date -&gt; select store -&gt; Enter name of the employee you want to see performance of. It will show total repairs made by selected employee for entered date. You can also view the repairs made by employee during specific time period by selecting custom range in calendar.
&ldquo;Repairs by employees&rdquo; Select &ldquo;Date&rdquo; and &ldquo;Store&rdquo; and click &ldquo;Search&rdquo;.

Email templates notify the customers of their appointment status. Admin can edit the email templates.
As an example, if an appointment is missed by the customer, admin can send the e-mail &ldquo;We miss you!&rdquo;
Even this e-mail template can be sent to all the no-show appointments.

Password can be changed and new changes will be sent automatically to Employee on his registered email.
To change the password:
Click &ldquo;Employees&rdquo; Search employee by &ldquo;Name&rdquo; or &ldquo;Email&rdquo; Click &ldquo;Change Password&rdquo; from &ldquo;Action&rdquo;
